                "content": {
                    "value": "<p>At Sinister Diesel, we\u2019re excited to offer great deals on our high-quality diesel parts. However, it\u2019s important to note that our sales are limited to <strong>Sinister Diesel-branded parts</strong> only.</p><h4><strong>What\u2019s Excluded?</strong></h4><p>Certain products are excluded from all sales, including:</p><ul><li><strong>Turbos</strong></li><li><strong>Fuel Pumps</strong></li><li><strong>Injectors</strong></li><li><strong>Clearance Items</strong></li><li><strong>Blemished Items</strong></li></ul><p>These exclusions are due to pricing agreements and manufacturing considerations.</p><p>We\u2019re committed to providing transparent and competitive pricing on all our products, whether they\u2019re on sale or not. If you have any questions about sale eligibility, feel free to reach out to our team.</p>"
